I think many people today

00:00:14.580 --> 00:00:15.990 align:middle line:84%
don't know what to
believe anymore.

00:00:15.990 --> 00:00:17.640 align:middle line:84%
>>People are basically
going to keep on

00:00:17.640 --> 00:00:20.740 align:middle line:84%
to help uncover what
really happened.

00:00:20.740 --> 00:00:22.830 align:middle line:84%
>>I felt like something
