sudden it gets bad.

00:59:05.824 --> 00:59:07.240 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Then it
gets mean, yeah.

00:59:07.240 --> 00:59:09.900 align:middle line:84%
>> GUILEY: And the personality
