00:59:22.070 --> 00:59:23.049 align:middle line:90%
with the other side?

00:59:23.049 --> 00:59:23.840 align:middle line:90%
>> GUILEY: It does.

00:59:23.840 --> 00:59:25.880 align:middle line:84%
This is one of my
favorite devices.

00:59:25.880 --> 00:59:29.700 align:middle line:84%
It's real time communication
with spirits and the dead.

00:59:29.700 --> 00:59:34.930 align:middle line:90%
And it's a radio scan device.

00:59:34.930 --> 00:59:36.320 align:middle line:90%
This is called a mini box.

00:59:36.320 --> 00:59:41.600 align:middle line:84%
And it runs on the
principle of a radio that

00:59:41.600 --> 00:59:43.590 align:middle line:84%
moves very fast up
and down the band,

00:59:43.590 --> 00:59:45.200 align:middle line:84%
like you would
take a manual tuner

00:59:45.200 --> 00:59:47.530 align:middle line:84%
and rip it up and down
the band very fast.

00:59:47.530 --> 00:59:49.900 align:middle line:84%
It creates a jumble
of noise that's

00:59:49.900 --> 00:59:53.270 align:middle line:84%
a background sound
that spirit voices have

00:59:53.270 --> 00:59:55.070 align:middle line:90%
the capability of manipulating.

00:59:55.070 --> 00:59:57.040 align:middle line:84%
And they speak on
top of that scan.

00:59:57.040 --> 00:59:57.940 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: And it comes
right through here.

00:59:57.940 --> 01:00:00.106 align:middle line:84%
>> GUILEY: And unfortunately,
in a studio like this,

01:00:00.106 --> 01:00:02.610 align:middle line:84%
we're not going to get
the reception to be able

01:00:02.610 --> 01:00:03.770 align:middle line:90%
to demonstrate it.

01:00:03.770 --> 01:00:06.680 align:middle line:84%
But I take this out on
my field investigations,

01:00:06.680 --> 01:00:10.220 align:middle line:84%
and I can have direct two-way
real time communication

01:00:10.220 --> 01:00:13.520 align:middle line:84%
with the dead and with beings
who identify themselves

01:00:13.520 --> 01:00:14.645 align:middle line:90%
as non-human personalities.

01:00:14.645 --> 01:00:16.510 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: And technology
has allowed us to do this.

01:00:16.510 --> 01:00:16.845 align:middle line:90%
>> GUILEY: Technology--

01:00:16.845 --> 01:00:17.620 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: This is amazing.

01:00:17.620 --> 01:00:18.703 align:middle line:90%
>> GUILEY: --is advancing.

