this emerging technology.

01:00:24.087 --> 01:00:24.795 align:middle line:90%
It's fascinating.

01:00:24.795 --> 01:00:25.628 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: I love it.

01:00:25.628 --> 01:00:28.440 align:middle line:84%
>> GUILEY: I think someday we
are going to get that proof

01:00:28.440 --> 01:00:31.000 align:middle line:84%
of the afterlife that
will be undeniable,

01:00:31.000 --> 01:00:33.400 align:middle line:84%
